⑤ Persist metadata → PostgreSQL
⑥ Unload model → free VRAM" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=9;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
